# Getting Started with Gauge
This is a context step that runs before every scenario
* Open localhost

## Must display card
* Add word "is it a kitty?" "Question"
* Add word "yes it is" "Answer"
* Click "Add"
* Must display "Question 1"
* Must display "is it a kitty?"

* Add word "is it a cat?" "Question"
* Add word "yes it does" "Answer"
* Click "Add"
* Must display "Question 1"
* Must display "is it a cat?"

